[[Image:Niger river map.PNG|thumb|right|Ing Azawagh ing bibilug king dakeng pangulu-aslagan ning [[Niger River basin]], dapot ngeni ing ilug Azawagh makaba ya ampong malangi, at ing lugal mikakadanum ya ibat kareng ilug king lalam gabun keraklan.]] 
Ing '''Azawagh''' ing pangkabilugan a lagiung e opisial para kareng manimunang dakeng mágsalitang [[Tuareg languages|Tamashek]] king [[pangulu]]ng [[Mali]], [[pangulu]]ng [[Niger]], ampong dake ning [[mauli]]ng [[Algeria]]. Bibilugan de reng [[Sahel]] ampong [[desiertong Sahara]], a keraklan misnang leparan a kapatagan nung nu la manuknang deng [[nomad]] ing Azawagh, nung nu la manuknangan deng [[nomad]] a Tuareg. E ne katulid o katumbas ning sanumang metung a labuad a administratibo o pangkapamahalan ning Mali, Niger o Algeria, oneng kayabe la keti deng labuad a [[Kidal]] ning Mali ampo reng labuad ning [[Tahoua]] ampong [[Agadez]] ning Niger, pati na reng as mangaragul a dake ning mauling  Algeria.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://english.aljazeera.net/focus/unrestsahara/2008/07/20087118508319575.html|title=Who are the Tuareg?|publisher=[[Al Jazeera]]|date=2008-07-14|accessdate=2008-07-14}}</ref> There are also groups of Tuareg peoples in [[Mauritania]], [[Libya]] and [[Burkina Faso]].{{Fact|date=February 2012}}

Atin yang masikan ampong makayaliwang pamikilala ing Azawagh a darala na ning lahing  [[Tuareg people|Tuareg]] a makayaliwa kareng opisial a pamikilala ampong kaurian da reng pangkalibudtan o sentral a kapamahalan da reng Mali, Niger ampong Algeria. Linto ya ing Azawagh antimong pisasabian o issue a geopolitical o pang heograpia politikal uli ning kapagnasan a separatista nung nu ing Mouvement Populaire pour la Libération de l'Azawad ampo ing mas bayung [[National Movement for the Liberation of Azawad]] a maki kapagnasan a mitátag magsarili o independienting republikang maki pamikilalang Tuareg.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://afribonemali.net/spip.php?article3693|title=Rébellion au Nord Mali, Comment Iyad Ag Ghali a repris le maquis|publisher=Afribone.com|date=2006-05-29|accessdate=2010-06-26}}</ref> Milyari murin iti uli ning [[War on Terror]].

